P2.4 Provider.go Tests Implementation
=====================================

Added 7 tests for provider.go functions:

1. TestAll_ReturnsProviders: Verifies All() returns at least one provider
2. TestAll_HasAWSProvider: Verifies AWS provider is in the list
3. TestAllWithStore_ReturnsProviders: Tests AllWithStore with valid store
4. TestAllWithStore_NilStore: Tests graceful degradation with nil store
5. TestProviderInterface_Implementation: Verifies AWSProvider implements Provider
6. TestTeardownProviderInterface: Verifies TeardownProvider implementation

Coverage:
- All(): 60% (error path during store creation not tested)
- AllWithStore(): 100%
- GetAWSProvider(): 100%

Note: All() error path at line 31-38 creates a store internally,
making it difficult to test the error case without dependency injection.
